Vaadin Lienzo Addon

 Enables Lienzo Panel to be used as an add-on for Vaadin 8 via Lienzo Structure Graphics GWT Toolkit

Getting started
 See the demo application included.

Workflow

 Add the dependency
  <dependency>
   <groupId>com.neotropic</groupId>
   <artifactId>vaadin-lienzo</artifactId>
   <version>0.</version>
  </dependency>
 
 GWT inherits
  <inherits name="com.neotropic.vaadin.lienzo.WidgetSet" />

Supported Features
 Add and Remove Background
 Add, Update and Remove Node Widgets
 Add, Update and Remove Edge Widgets
 Add, Update and Remove Frame Widgets

Supported Events

 Lienzo Component Mouse Over

 Node Widget Click
 Node Widget Right Click
 Node Widget Double Click
 Node Widget Update
 
 Edge Widget Click
 Edge Widget Right Click
 Edge Widget Double Click
 Edge Widget Update

 Frame Widget Click
 Frame Widget Right Click
 Frame Widget Double Click 
 Frame Widget Update
